      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of rare distinction, this specimen remains in flawless, showroom condition. Meticulously curated and maintained to the highest standards, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine interior to the immaculate mechanical components, reflects a legacy of absolute preservation. This is an unparalleled opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends standard market offerings in both aesthetic and functional excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
