      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is the one! Come take a look, you\u2019re gonna love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44800.0,
