    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the iconic S54 inline-six engine, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated double-VANOS system. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring a proactively reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec bushings with zero deflection. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. The valvetrain is quiet, compression is optimal across all cylinders, and the undercarriage is devoid of any fluid seepage or oxidation. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
